# ============================================================
# 高翠网 .gitignore
# ============================================================

# ===== 敏感配置 / 密钥 (切勿提交!) =====
# 后端环境配置含: OSS AccessKey/Secret、DashScope API Key、数据库密码
**/application-dev.yml
**/application-local.yml
**/application-prod.yml
**/application-*local*.yml
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# 保留示例模板, 供他人参考结构
!**/application-dev.yml.example

# ===== IDE =====
.idea/
.vscode/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
*.swp
.project
.classpath
.settings/

# ===== OS =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ===== 后端 (Java / Maven / Spring Boot) =====
**/target/
**/build/
*.class
# 构建产物 jar/war (保留 pom 引用的依赖)
/*.jar
/*.war
*.log
hs_err_pid*

# ===== 前端 (Node / Vite) =====
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
*.local
.pnpm-store/
.pnpm-debug.log*
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.vite/
coverage/
